1
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:07,480
All men must die, some deaths weigh more than others.

2
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:10,000
But I never imagined

3
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,959
that I'd lose my head

4
00:01:11,959 --> 00:01:14,400
over a "useless prince who won't be emperor."

5
00:01:15,159 --> 00:01:15,959
Hmm.

6
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:19,400
You there.

7
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,599
Before you die,

8
00:01:21,760 --> 00:01:23,519
do you have any last words?

9
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:28,920
I have one thing to say.

10
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:29,560
Got it, behead him.

11
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:30,159
Roger, beheading him.

12
00:01:30,159 --> 00:01:30,760
Off with his head!

13
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,040
Hey, hey, hey!

14
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:31,920
I haven't even spoken yet!

15
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,359
I still...

16
00:01:32,359 --> 00:01:32,799
This, this...

17
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:34,079
This doesn't count!

18
00:01:38,799 --> 00:01:39,599
Presenting!

19
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,280
Ouyang Yan of Dayan...

20
00:01:41,280 --> 00:01:43,000
and Ouyang Que, for an audience!

21
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,959
Greetings, Your Majesty.

22
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:57,239
You two,

23
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,000
please rise.

24
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,040
Thank you, Your Majesty.

25
00:02:02,519 --> 00:02:03,519
My dear ministers,

26
00:02:04,439 --> 00:02:05,760
our Daliang Kingdom

27
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:08,120
has long been friendly with the Dayan Kingdom.

28
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:10,319
Today, on my son's birthday,

29
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,240
I hereby announce

30
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:14,439
that from this day forward,

31
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:18,360
the Dayan Kingdom and Daliang Kingdom shall form a marriage alliance,

32
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,599
united forever.

33
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:22,039
Wise is our Emperor!

34
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:25,879
Your Majesty,

35
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,000
my father has fallen ill and cannot attend.

36
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:29,680
So I shall present my sister in his stead.

37
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:31,479
I hope Your Majesty

38
00:02:31,759 --> 00:02:33,199
and the Crown Prince will forgive us.

39
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,360
My sister is rather unruly.

40
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,159
From now on,

41
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:38,560
I ask Your Highness to please bear with her.

42
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,280
Not at all, not at all.

43
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,479
Please, take your seats.

44
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:44,159
Thank you, Your Majesty.

45
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,680
My son,

46
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:52,439
shouldn't we pick an auspicious day soon

47
00:02:53,039 --> 00:02:56,039
so all the people of the realm can celebrate

48
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:56,919
this happy occasion with you?

49
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:01,680
Father,

50
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:04,840
your child does not wish to marry.

51
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:15,759
Doesn't wish to marry?

52
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,080
Throughout the ages,

53
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,800
one must build a family and rule the state

54
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,039
before pacifying the world.

55
00:03:24,039 --> 00:03:25,639
As the Crown Prince,

56
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,879
if you don't marry,

57
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,560
how will you produce an heir

58
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:30,840
to inherit the throne?

59
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:39,680
Father,

60
00:03:40,719 --> 00:03:42,400
your child stayed awake thinking all night,

61
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,840
and must tell you the truth.

62
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,319
The truth?

63
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:51,479
What truth?

64
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,479
Father,

65
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,599
what is the real reason?

66
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,520
Tell your father.

67
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:02,520
I'm actually

68
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:03,840
quite an open-minded man.

69
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:07,599
Your child...

70
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:11,039
Your child simply doesn't want to be Emperor.

71
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,399
Doesn't want to be Emperor?!

72
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:20,600
In all the world,

73
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,959
is there a Crown Prince who doesn't want the throne?

74
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,360
Father,

75
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,120
because your child has other dreams.

76
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,360
Hahahaha!

77
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:30,319
You little brat,

78
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,839
I think you've

79
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:35,759
lost your mind!

80
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,279
Guards!

81
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,279
Bring out all that ridiculous junk of his

82
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,720
and haul it in here!

83
00:04:50,959 --> 00:04:51,759
Out of my way!

84
00:04:52,639 --> 00:04:54,120
These are works by famous comic artists.

85
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,399
Don't slander them, all right?

86
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,160
I told you long ago

87
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:02,600
to burn all these things around him.

88
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:03,959
Why are they still here?

89
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,680
What's the matter with you?

90
00:05:06,959 --> 00:05:08,240
Who's attending the Crown Prince?

91
00:05:08,399 --> 00:05:09,519
Bring them here!

92
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,160
Kneel!

93
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,160
You two,

94
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:21,120
do you know your crime?

95
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,639
Take them away!

96
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:24,720
Father,

97
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,279
this has nothing to do with them.

98
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:27,959
It's your child.

99
00:05:29,079 --> 00:05:30,600
Your child is truly lacking in talent.

100
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:33,000
I can't understand the Confucian classics,

101
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,920
nor can I learn the way of governing.

102
00:05:36,279 --> 00:05:37,240
Only these comics

103
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,600
can relieve a bit of my worries.

104
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:41,959
I beg you, Father,

105
00:05:42,279 --> 00:05:42,920
spare your child.

106
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,600
Don't make your child inherit the throne.

107
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,519
What nonsense are you talking about?

108
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:47,439
Huh?

109
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:50,240
What Crown Prince doesn't want to be Emperor?

110
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:56,879
Father,

111
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,480
then your child wants to be the first.

112
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:05,399
Hey, hey!

113
00:06:06,839 --> 00:06:07,199
Hey!

114
00:06:07,199 --> 00:06:08,079
Why are you here?

115
00:06:09,079 --> 00:06:10,879
The Crown Prince's Enthronement ceremony is near.

116
00:06:11,319 --> 00:06:12,800
Eunuch Gao ordered

117
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,199
to slaughter this Western speckled hen

118
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,879
for the Crown Prince,

119
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,000
to nourish his body.

120
00:06:18,079 --> 00:06:18,199
Hey!

121
00:06:19,279 --> 00:06:20,800
Didn't we already agree?

122
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,319
We must wait until Huahua is fully grown

123
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:25,279
to get its maximum nutritional value.

124
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,079
Bullshit!

125
00:06:27,519 --> 00:06:28,920
We've already checked.

126
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,360
That was all nonsense you made up.

127
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:31,680
This chicken

128
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,399
should've been killed long ago!

129
00:06:33,399 --> 00:06:33,680
Hey!

130
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,160
Hey!

131
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,120
You can't!

132
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,279
You can't take my chicken!

133
00:06:36,639 --> 00:06:37,480
Let go of me!

134
00:06:39,879 --> 00:06:40,720
Let go!

135
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,519
I won't!

136
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,199
With two more keepers like you in the palace,

137
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:45,439
will we ever get to eat chicken?

138
00:06:45,439 --> 00:06:46,240
No!

139
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:53,199
The chicken I'm protecting is named Huahua.

140
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,399
It was born under my watch.

141
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:55,920
And I

142
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:57,120
am just a chicken keeper.

143
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,240
But in the palace,

144
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:01,079
even someone like me was given a title:

145
00:07:01,759 --> 00:07:03,079
Royal Chicken Keeper.

146
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,399
You've finally hatched.

147
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,759
From now on, we only have each other.

148
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,360
I'll protect you.

149
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:16,279
I raised Huahua with my own hands.

150
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:18,279
It's my only family.

151
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:21,199
It snuggles in my bed to keep me warm.

152
00:07:21,439 --> 00:07:23,600
No one else has ever treated me this way.

153
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,199
Every day it's with me,

154
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:27,040
I sleep soundly.

155
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,240
The Crown Prince has escaped!

156
00:07:33,519 --> 00:07:34,279
Oh no!

157
00:07:34,839 --> 00:07:36,759
The Crown Prince has escaped!

158
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:37,639
Huahua,

159
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,839
our chance has come!

160
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,079
Huahua,

161
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,279
Once we leave the palace,

162
00:07:59,279 --> 00:08:00,399
we'll be free.

163
00:08:02,079 --> 00:08:02,279
Hey!

164
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,040
My Huahua! My comics!

165
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:06,120
Move your foot, you're stepping on my book!

166
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:06,720
Sorry, sorry!

167
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:10,360
Don't get me wrong.

168
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,839
This wasn't love at first sight.

169
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,399
I have a certain ability.

170
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:16,439
I was born able to see things I'd rather not.

171
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:19,240
Just let your child go.

172
00:08:24,079 --> 00:08:25,000
Fine!

173
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,360
If you dare take one step out of this palace gate,

174
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:31,480
I'll strip you of the Crown Prince title forever!

175
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:33,240
You'll live as a commoner for life!

176
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:36,600
Father.

177
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,960
Is it really that simple?

178
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:43,840
Father,

179
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,440
please forgive your unfilial child.

180
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:47,679
Hey!

181
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:48,240
Crown Prince!

182
00:08:48,799 --> 00:08:49,320
Crown Prince!

183
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:50,039
Crown Prince!

184
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:51,600
Hey!

185
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,360
Crown Prince!

186
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,240
Hey!

187
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,159
Hey!

188
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:58,919
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

189
00:08:59,519 --> 00:08:59,919
Your Majesty!

190
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,000
Your Majesty!

191
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:04,240
Your Majesty!

192
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,360
What's wrong, Your Majesty?

193
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,679
You're the Crown Prince.

194
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,399
You're escaping?

195
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,320
You're a guard, aren't you?

196
00:09:13,799 --> 00:09:14,720
I'm the Royal Chicken Keeper.

197
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:16,480
I'm escaping too.

198
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:19,519
Wonderful!

199
00:09:20,120 --> 00:09:20,799
Then let's run together.

200
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,960
Crown Prince, please spare me!

201
00:09:23,399 --> 00:09:24,879
On my own, I'd have a slim chance.

202
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:27,080
You've already failed 101 times.

203
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:28,679
No way.

204
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:29,879
You must cover for me.

205
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,120
Or I'll execute your entire clan, believe it!

206
00:09:31,559 --> 00:09:32,600
You're scaring me to death!

207
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,000
You're not even going to be Emperor.

208
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,399
You've no right to execute my clan.

209
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,799
Not bad, chicken keeper.

210
00:09:37,799 --> 00:09:39,240
You're quite cultured.

211
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:41,080
I am an imperial scholar.

212
00:09:41,639 --> 00:09:43,080
I was being sarcastic.

213
00:09:43,639 --> 00:09:44,600
You all, go that way!

214
00:09:44,799 --> 00:09:46,360
Don't miss a single corner!

215
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,279
Search thoroughly!

216
00:09:56,919 --> 00:09:58,200
He was just here.

217
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,200
Huahua,

218
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:03,080
I'll definitely protect you.

219
00:10:03,519 --> 00:10:04,440
That's strange.

220
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:06,039
You!

221
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:07,159
Go that way!

222
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:08,799
All of you, go that way!

223
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:13,840
Chicken keeper!

224
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,879
You've doomed me!

225
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:17,440
Hey!

226
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:18,000
Crown Prince!

227
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:19,799
Crown Prince!

228
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,039
Halt!

229
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:26,559
Huahua,

230
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,440
from now on, we...

231
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:47,279
Halt!

232
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:48,840
Who goes there?

233
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:52,240
I'm Qi Zhi, the Royal Chicken Keeper.

234
00:10:55,799 --> 00:10:57,200
You're just a chicken keeper.

235
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,639
What are you doing at the Crown Prince's hall?

236
00:10:59,159 --> 00:10:59,600
Get out of here, now.

237
00:11:03,759 --> 00:11:04,279
Huahua!

238
00:11:05,039 --> 00:11:06,200
I won't give up on you!

239
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:13,840
What are you doing?

240
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:14,600
Let go!

241
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:15,559
Let go!

242
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:16,639
Let go!

243
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:18,559
You actually like wearing women's undergarments?

244
00:11:18,559 --> 00:11:19,120
That's nonsense!

245
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:19,480
Guards!

246
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:19,840
Seize him!

247
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:20,600
Embroidered with mandarin ducks.

248
00:11:22,759 --> 00:11:23,200
Heh heh.

249
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,440
How did you know?

250
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:27,120
You were just thinking all about yesterday.

251
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:28,879
Want me to share more details?

252
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,039
Shhh!

253
00:11:33,399 --> 00:11:34,320
You're ruthless.

254
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:34,639
Speak.

255
00:11:34,879 --> 00:11:35,600
What do you want?

256
00:11:37,559 --> 00:11:38,919
I want to see the Crown Prince.

257
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:41,159
You'd better give up that idea.

258
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,240
I'm not going to take the throne.

259
00:11:43,639 --> 00:11:44,159
It's you!

260
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:45,600
Where's Huahua?

261
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:46,240
Where are my comics?

262
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:48,799
They're all right here.

263
00:11:48,799 --> 00:11:49,960
Chicken for books, fair trade.

264
00:11:52,759 --> 00:11:53,320
The chicken isn't here.

265
00:11:56,159 --> 00:11:57,639
Did you stew it?

266
00:11:57,639 --> 00:11:58,240
I didn't stew it.

267
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,279
I hid it away.

268
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:01,440
You're lying!

269
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:02,200
I'm not.

270
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,919
Help me escape.

271
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:05,360
And I'll return Huahua to you, deal?

272
00:12:21,399 --> 00:12:22,200
Hey.

273
00:12:22,759 --> 00:12:23,759
How do we escape?

274
00:12:23,759 --> 00:12:25,039
First, let me check my comics.

275
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,960
The books are all there, every last one.

276
00:12:27,159 --> 00:12:28,240
Just tell me how to escape.

277
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,399
You and I...

278
00:12:29,679 --> 00:12:30,200
swap clothes.

279
00:12:30,679 --> 00:12:31,440
Once I've escaped,

280
00:12:31,639 --> 00:12:32,039
then you escape.

281
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:33,679
Crown Prince.

282
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,320
You've used this method before.

283
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:37,519
Over thirty eunuchs have been flogged because of it.

284
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:39,919
Can you please come to your senses?

285
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,399
This time it'll definitely work.

286
00:12:41,919 --> 00:12:43,039
Since Father's passing,

287
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:44,360
the palace security isn't what it used to be.

288
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,480
Read my lips.

289
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,639
No way.

290
00:12:50,679 --> 00:12:51,200
Fine.

291
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:52,879
Then get ready to drink chicken soup.

292
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:57,519
Swap!

293
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:08,919
The young Prince has arrived!

294
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,039
Father!

295
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:19,039
Your child has arrived too late!

296
00:13:21,039 --> 00:13:21,840
Father!

297
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,559
Twenty-Eighth Prince,

298
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:25,000
please accept my condolences.

299
00:13:38,159 --> 00:13:39,440
By the late Emperor's decree,

300
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,399
before the Crown Prince ascends the throne,

301
00:13:41,879 --> 00:13:44,879
I shall handle all court affairs in his stead.

302
00:13:46,240 --> 00:13:47,360
I ask all of you, my lords,

303
00:13:48,399 --> 00:13:49,120
for your full cooperation.

304
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:56,919
Prince.

305
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:59,240
If the Prince wishes to speak, just speak.

306
00:13:59,639 --> 00:14:02,279
Why have musicians play while you do?

307
00:14:06,080 --> 00:14:07,759
Having your own background music...

308
00:14:09,679 --> 00:14:10,120
Never mind, let's not get into it.

309
00:14:12,279 --> 00:14:13,039
Back to the matter at hand.

310
00:14:14,279 --> 00:14:15,519
Father has ordered me to govern in his place.

311
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:17,720
What do all of you lords think of that?

312
00:14:27,519 --> 00:14:28,000
Hey.

313
00:14:28,639 --> 00:14:29,559
Under the cover of night,

314
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:31,759
this is the perfect chance to seduce the Crown Prince.

315
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,480
Once I'm carrying the Imperial heir,

316
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,759
I'll be made Empress.

317
00:14:35,559 --> 00:14:36,039
Father,

318
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:37,240
the revival of our Dayan Kingdom

319
00:14:37,480 --> 00:14:38,200
is right around the corner.

320
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:40,919
I'm off then.

321
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,080
Ah!

322
00:14:49,519 --> 00:14:50,320
Your Highness!

323
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:51,519
I'm a fan of your comics.

324
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,440
I know you love drawing comics.

325
00:14:53,879 --> 00:14:54,159
I...

326
00:14:54,559 --> 00:14:55,879
I'll be your model.

327
00:14:57,759 --> 00:14:59,120
Wherever you want to draw,

328
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:01,480
draw away.

329
00:15:02,039 --> 00:15:02,840
Hey, hey, hey!

330
00:15:03,159 --> 00:15:04,360
I'll be straight with you, my lady.

331
00:15:04,879 --> 00:15:05,559
The Crown Prince has fled.

332
00:15:05,879 --> 00:15:06,480
He's gone!

333
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,320
Hahahaha!

334
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:13,399
You're so funny.

335
00:15:13,559 --> 00:15:15,240
Isn't that laugh a bit too hearty?

336
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:20,519
Your Highness,

337
00:15:20,639 --> 00:15:21,639
no need to be shy.

338
00:15:22,159 --> 00:15:23,320
The night is long,

339
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:23,919
so why not...

340
00:15:24,279 --> 00:15:26,480
on this last night before your enthronement,

341
00:15:26,919 --> 00:15:27,879
let me keep you company.

342
00:15:28,960 --> 00:15:29,559
Help!

343
00:15:29,559 --> 00:15:29,960
Hey!

344
00:15:30,519 --> 00:15:32,519
Your strength is ridiculous!

345
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,960
I love men like you.

346
00:15:35,519 --> 00:15:36,799
The kind this Princess

347
00:15:36,799 --> 00:15:39,039
can never fail to get.

348
00:15:42,039 --> 00:15:44,200
Help! She's molesting me!

349
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:44,679
I...

350
00:15:44,679 --> 00:15:45,720
The Crown Prince has run away!

351
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,159
What?

352
00:15:47,559 --> 00:15:48,639
You're not the Crown Prince?

353
00:15:49,279 --> 00:15:51,279
I told you I'm not the Crown Prince.

354
00:15:52,519 --> 00:15:53,879
How dare you molest me!

355
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:54,559
Ah!

356
00:15:54,879 --> 00:15:55,559
Pervert!

357
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,039
Pervert!

358
00:16:01,159 --> 00:16:01,840
Pervert!

359
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:03,759
Who are you people?

360
00:16:05,799 --> 00:16:06,799
And who are you?

361
00:16:08,159 --> 00:16:09,360
You don't even recognize me?

362
00:16:13,440 --> 00:16:13,759
Hey!

363
00:16:14,519 --> 00:16:15,879
Why are you wearing the Crown Prince's clothes?

364
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:18,440
So, you dare impersonate the Crown Prince!

365
00:16:20,039 --> 00:16:20,720
I'm just passing through.

366
00:16:20,799 --> 00:16:21,519
You two carry on.

367
00:16:21,559 --> 00:16:22,360
Wait!

368
00:16:26,240 --> 00:16:28,120
I am the Princess of the Dayan Kingdom.

369
00:16:28,559 --> 00:16:29,440
What are you trying to do?

370
00:16:31,159 --> 00:16:32,679
You're the Princess of the Dayan Kingdom?

371
00:16:32,679 --> 00:16:34,320
And I'm a Prince of the Daliang Kingdom!

372
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:35,480
Hey!

373
00:16:36,039 --> 00:16:37,120
The two of you,

374
00:16:37,159 --> 00:16:39,559
sneaking into the Crown Prince's chambers at night,

375
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,360
what are you up to?

376
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:42,399
Guards!

377
00:16:43,000 --> 00:16:43,759
Seize them!

378
00:16:43,759 --> 00:16:44,559
Yes, sir!

379
00:16:47,879 --> 00:16:48,960
After them, hurry!

380
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,759
It's a misunderstanding!

381
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:58,360
Before you die,

382
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,360
do you have any last words?

383
00:17:04,640 --> 00:17:05,839
I have one thing to say.

384
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:06,559
Hmm?

385
00:17:06,759 --> 00:17:07,119
Got it.

386
00:17:07,359 --> 00:17:07,680
Behead him!

387
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:08,079
Hey, hey, hey!

388
00:17:08,079 --> 00:17:09,039
I haven't even spoken yet!

389
00:17:09,039 --> 00:17:09,480
I still...

390
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:09,960
This, this...

391
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,279
This doesn't count!

392
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:24,119
How dare you!

393
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:26,079
You dare raid the execution ground?

394
00:17:26,519 --> 00:17:29,119
How can you raid the execution ground without even shouting "Stay the blade"?

395
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,400
I don't know your Daliang customs.

396
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,359
But this man, today...

397
00:17:35,119 --> 00:17:36,519
you cannot kill.

398
00:17:37,319 --> 00:17:38,240
On what grounds?

399
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:39,480
On what grounds?

400
00:17:40,440 --> 00:17:41,079
On the grounds...

401
00:17:41,599 --> 00:17:43,400
that I'm a Princess of the Dayan Kingdom.

402
00:17:44,279 --> 00:17:44,680
On the grounds...

403
00:17:45,559 --> 00:17:47,440
that I have diplomatic immunity.

404
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:48,960
And on the grounds...

405
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,839
that this Princess wants to save him.

406
00:17:51,559 --> 00:17:52,000
How about that?

407
00:17:54,400 --> 00:17:55,359
Princess Ouyang,

408
00:17:55,799 --> 00:17:57,480
even with diplomatic immunity,

409
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,960
you can't run wild in our Daliang Kingdom.

410
00:18:00,440 --> 00:18:01,039
Guards!

411
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:02,960
Behead the prisoner, Qi Zhi!

412
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:04,160
Hey!

413
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:05,119
Don't save me anymore.

414
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,720
I won't let you become my Empress.

415
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:07,359
Just go, quickly!

416
00:18:07,839 --> 00:18:08,960
I'm not here to save you.

417
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:10,680
How dare you molest me!

418
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:11,799
If you must die,

419
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,799
you'll die by my hand!

420
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:16,759
Me, molest you?

421
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:17,400
Hey!

422
00:18:18,240 --> 00:18:21,160
Condemning a random chicken keeper in the palace,

423
00:18:21,720 --> 00:18:22,680
what kind of skill is that?

424
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,400
You Daliang folks just bully honest people.

425
00:18:28,519 --> 00:18:30,000
She actually has a point.

426
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,319
But that's exactly what we're doing.

427
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:33,119
So what?

428
00:18:33,599 --> 00:18:34,480
Bite me!

429
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:35,759
Seize her!

430
00:19:02,079 --> 00:19:02,400
Hey!

431
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:03,720
What are you doing?

432
00:19:03,839 --> 00:19:04,920
Hurry up and behead the prisoner!

433
00:19:07,079 --> 00:19:07,680
Who dares to touch him?

434
00:19:11,599 --> 00:19:12,640
Crown Prince!

435
00:19:25,759 --> 00:19:26,359
Eunuch Gao,

436
00:19:26,759 --> 00:19:27,400
announce the decree.

437
00:19:27,799 --> 00:19:28,640
I've returned to take the throne.

438
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:31,839
Really, Your Highness?

439
00:19:33,480 --> 00:19:34,039
Your Majesty!

440
00:19:34,319 --> 00:19:34,880
Your Majesty!

441
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:40,839
Long live the Emperor!

442
00:19:41,079 --> 00:19:41,880
Long live!

443
00:19:46,839 --> 00:19:47,240
Summon...

444
00:19:47,599 --> 00:19:49,119
the Royal Chicken Keeper,

445
00:19:49,119 --> 00:19:51,200
Qi Zhi, for an audience!

446
00:20:01,359 --> 00:20:02,359
Your servant, Qi Zhi,

447
00:20:02,359 --> 00:20:03,680
greets Your Majesty.

448
00:20:05,759 --> 00:20:06,559
Rise.

449
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:07,519
Thank you, Your Majesty.

450
00:20:09,279 --> 00:20:09,839
Chicken keeper,

451
00:20:10,559 --> 00:20:10,960
I know.

452
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,400
You're an imperial scholar,

453
00:20:12,759 --> 00:20:14,000
deeply learned,

454
00:20:14,519 --> 00:20:16,920
yet you've been raising palace chickens.

455
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:18,480
That's truly a waste of your talents.

456
00:20:19,279 --> 00:20:20,440
I summoned you here today

457
00:20:20,559 --> 00:20:21,359
because I hope

458
00:20:21,759 --> 00:20:23,960
you can shoulder a great responsibility for the court.

459
00:20:28,039 --> 00:20:28,440
Your Majesty,

460
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,559
I have always held

461
00:20:30,559 --> 00:20:32,359
the vision of a wise ruler and able minister.

462
00:20:32,559 --> 00:20:34,000
Now that I have Your Majesty's favor,

463
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:34,640
I shall surely

464
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:36,000
devote myself entirely,

465
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:37,000
until my dying breath.

466
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:38,720
Excellent.

467
00:20:39,839 --> 00:20:40,279
I hereby decree:

468
00:20:41,039 --> 00:20:41,720
Qi Zhi is appointed

469
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:42,960
as Secret Imperial Commissioner,

470
00:20:43,839 --> 00:20:44,240
to find for me

471
00:20:44,519 --> 00:20:46,000
a suitable heir to the throne,

472
00:20:46,480 --> 00:20:47,839
and within three months.

473
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:48,839
I

474
00:20:49,359 --> 00:20:50,079
shall abdicate at once.

475
00:20:50,519 --> 00:20:51,279
All state affairs

476
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,599
shall be handled by the cabinet.

477
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:53,480
What?!

478
00:21:09,279 --> 00:21:09,720
Huahua!

479
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:10,960
You snuck Huahua out!

480
00:21:11,319 --> 00:21:12,240
I'm coming with you.

481
00:21:12,759 --> 00:21:13,480
What?

482
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:15,039
You

483
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:16,720
want to find the heir to the throne.

484
00:21:17,119 --> 00:21:17,359
I

485
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:18,400
want to be Empress.

486
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,920
I don't care who becomes Emperor.

487
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:22,039
Whoever inherits the throne

488
00:21:22,279 --> 00:21:22,920
has to marry me

489
00:21:23,240 --> 00:21:24,160
and make me his Empress.

490
00:21:26,119 --> 00:21:27,240
So I'm going with you.

491
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:27,880
Save your breath.

492
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:29,039
With your personality,

493
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:30,000
even after we find the Prince,

494
00:21:30,400 --> 00:21:31,240
nobody would want to marry you.

495
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:31,640
Oh.

496
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:32,480
Really?

497
00:21:36,839 --> 00:21:38,559
"One Hundred Ways to Cook Chicken."

498
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:40,920
Four ounces of chicken,

499
00:21:40,960 --> 00:21:42,200
wash clean, add salt,

500
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,960
and a pinch of sugar.

501
00:21:44,039 --> 00:21:44,640
Fine, you win.

502
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:45,440
Let's go together.

503
00:21:46,759 --> 00:21:48,039
Want it back, huh?

504
00:21:48,759 --> 00:21:50,000
Once I become Empress,

505
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:51,039
I'll naturally give it back.

506
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:53,319
Hey!

507
00:22:00,599 --> 00:22:01,400
Huahua!

508
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:20,480
Trying to find other heirs?

509
00:22:21,359 --> 00:22:22,519
In your dreams.

510
00:22:23,240 --> 00:22:24,319
When that time comes,

511
00:22:24,640 --> 00:22:28,079
they'll all become stepping stones on my path to success.
